{"tid":1804703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西營盤女子墮樓斃命","createTime":"2019-12-31T07:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T10:28:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa92d20c846686c30f69734d8e7b0c6f4d6f3a7","tid":1804703,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"西營盤有人從高處墮下，今日(31日)中午12時09分，警方接獲市民報案，指皇后大道西235號，傳出巨響後發現一名中年女子昏迷不醒倒臥於大廈對開後巷，懷疑從高處墮下。消防及救護員接報到場，惟經檢查後證實女子已經傷重不治。<br />\n警方正設法聯絡死者家屬，了解其身世背景及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n 醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=8b0768a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191231/bkn-20191231125251999-1231_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5191750404ea26eac7568a5e998dd6bbf23ac8cc","tid":1804703,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"德美聯署整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"a8a39bbc40083a096b1a4840a5854e20b7ca539b","tid":1804703,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n藍屍？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d83832a58f825d6479e473f899467fe6bc718e9c","tid":1804703,"uid":311062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8a39bbc40083a096b1a4840a5854e20b7ca539b","tid":1804703,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"